      <title>电动汽车出口受创 中国车企寻求延长补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-auto-body-seeks-subsidy-extension-as-ev-exports-take-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的汽车制造商行业组织呼吁政府延长旧车交易优惠政策，作为在电动汽车出口下滑的情况下刺激国内汽车销售的措施之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-auto-body-seeks-subsidy-extension-as-ev-exports-take-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀数据比股市表现更重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然抗通胀的斗争可能基本取得了胜利，但价格压力带来的紧张局势仍可能破坏人们对降息的信心。股市似乎对这些警告视而不见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
