      <title>中国市场谨慎，关键政策会议希望减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-markets-flag-caution-reduced-hope-for-key-policy-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国市场再次出现一种熟悉的怀疑情绪，股市涨势快速消退，表明人们对此次重要政策会议能否出台当局承诺的那种有力增长刺激措施的预期较低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-markets-flag-caution-reduced-hope-for-key-policy-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
